Global Cordless Garden Equipment Market

The cordless garden equipment market is expected to witness market growth at a rate of approximately 4.00% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on cordless garden equipment market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecast period while providing their impacts on the marketâ€™s growth. The rising gardening activities in residential complexes are escalating the growth of the cordless garden equipment market.

Cordless garden equipment refers to tools which work on extra power source and employ mechanisms other than manual labor or hand tools. The most common type of power tools are electric motors. These tools are utilized for gardening and overlaps with the range of tools made for agriculture and horticulture. This sort of equipment could be used anywhere and anytime owning to lightweight and designed for comfort and ease of use on long shifts. They are known to meet even the most stringent environmental regulations and there is no requirement for petrol.

The growth in awareness among the people regarding environmental protection, rising demand of landscaping services in emerging economies and increasing housing activities are the major factors driving the cordless garden equipment market. The increase in popularity of the products among consumers because they are long-lasting and reliable battery and requirement of minimal service or maintenance equipment due to their ability of being charged fully or partially over a hundred times, without any significance loss of capacity accelerate the cordless garden equipment market growth. The rise in number of research and development activities, increase in investment in research projects and the introduction of multipurpose as well as high recital products by manufacturers influence the cordless garden equipment market. Additionally, governments of various countries emphasize on providing subsidies and schemes to consumers who are involved in gardening, rise in automation in various industries and agricultural activity and use of cordless machinery because of unavailability of farm labor and high cost of labor positively affect the cordless garden equipment market. Furthermore, technological advancement and innovations in product to enhance the performance and their application extend profitable opportunities to the cordless garden equipment market players in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

On the other hand, high cost associated with the product and maintenance is expected to obstruct the cordless garden equipment market growth. The complexity in the replacement operations is projected to challenge the cordless garden equipment market in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

